{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"12-mota-raja-patla-kutta","title":"ਮੋਟਾ  ਰਾਜਾ ਪਤਲਾ ਕੁੱਤਾ","description":"ਮੋਟੇ ਰਾਜੇ ਦੇ ਨਾਲ਼ ਪਤਲੇ ਕੁੱਤੇ ਪਿੱਛੇ ਭੱਜੋ!","language":"Punjabi","langCode":"pa","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"portrait","authors":["S. Waqeel"],"illustrators":["Parismita"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/12-mota-raja-patla-kutta"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/721909/size3/578f72502f01ea8298384a08257557b2.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/721909/size6/578f72502f01ea8298384a08257557b2.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/114/size6/7084a8068c9a42b2b038bfb5e8c8db83.jpg","text":"ਇਹ ਹੈ ਮੋਟਾ ਰਾਜਾ।","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/115/size6/fc2435f5701ae9603cc6785dcb09b219.jpg","text":"ਮੋਟੇ ਰਾਜੇ ਦਾ ਹੈ ਪਤਲਾ ਕੁੱਤਾ।\nਮੋਟਾ ਰਾਜਾ ਅਤੇ ਪਤਲਾ ਕੁੱਤਾ ਘੁੰਮਣ ਨਿਕਲ਼ੇ।","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/116/size6/2ba83939aad00e2e38ac7d7dc4455098.jpg","text":"ਪਤਲੇ ਕੁੱਤੇ ਨੇ ਚਿੜੀ ਦੇਖੀ।\nਉਹ ਉਸ ਦੇ ਪਿੱਛੇ ਭੱਜਿਆ।","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/117/size6/bbb0c6f83740b05d6961531b68dbb035.jpg","text":"ਮੋਟਾ ਰਾਜਾ ਪਤਲੇ ਕੁੱਤੇ ਦੇ ਪਿੱਛੇ ਭੱਜਿਆ।","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/118/size6/929b633d19a25601efff30e9bd4f153f.jpg","text":"ਦੋਵੇਂ ਭੱਜੇ।\nਕਈ ਦਿਨਾਂ ਤੱਕ ਭੱਜਦੇ ਰਹੇ।","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/119/size6/816a8ceb403815fa792daaa9b707eab7.jpg","text":"ਮੋਟੇ ਰਾਜੇ ਨੇ ਪਤਲੇ ਕੁੱਤੇ ਨੂੰ ਫੜ ਹੀ ਲਿਆ।","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/120/size6/017b018ac241775c73741d03244edc9d.jpg","text":"ਮੋਟਾ ਰਾਜਾ ਹੁਣ ਪਤਲਾ ਹੈ।","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":7,"words":55}}